A zero minimum length is intentionally permitted (\enquote{keep every
token}); the negative case is the one that has no sensible meaning, so
we make sure it fails loudly.

<<test functions>>=

def test_word_cloud_question_requires_non_negative_min_length():
    with pytest.raises(ValueError):
