The word-cloud round trip checks two properties at once: every
presentation field survives the JSON detour, and the
[[extra_stop_words]] list is rebuilt as a tuple --- without the
coercion, the frozen dataclass would refuse to hash and any later
use in a set or dictionary would fail.

